# 🛠️ Personal Kanban Workflow Manager - MERN Stack
# Command + Shift + V

A solo-use Kanban-style workflow/task manager built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) with a clean UI and drag-and-drop functionality.

---

## ✅ Feature Checklist

### 📁 Boards
- [x] Create multiple boards (e.g., “Personal Goals”, “Work Tasks”, “Side Projects”)
- [x] Rename boards
- [x] Delete boards

### 📊 Kanban Columns
- [x] Default columns: To Do / In Progress / Done
- [x] Allow adding custom column names
- [x] Reorder columns (optional but nice)

### 📝 Tasks
- [x] Title + description
- [x] Drag and drop tasks between columns
- [x] Add tags or priority (Low / Medium / High)

### 🎯 Progress Tracking
- [x] Progress indicator (e.g., % of done tasks per board)

### 🌐 MongoDB Integration
- [x] Store all board and task data in MongoDB
- [x] API to fetch, create, update, and delete tasks/boards

### 🎨 UI/UX
- [ ] Clean and responsive UI
- [ ] Implement drag-and-drop (DnD Kit or React Beautiful DnD)

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, Tailwind CSS, Zustand or Context API, DnD Kit
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express
- **Database:** MongoDB (with Mongoose)
- **State Persistence:** MongoDB or local fallback